    <title>New Java Feature - Foreign Memory API</title>
    <link href="https://blog.zhongmingmao.top/2025/01/16/new-java-feature-foreign-memory-api/"/>
    <id>https://blog.zhongmingmao.top/2025/01/16/new-java-feature-foreign-memory-api/</id>
